    "Previous research has found that students who are more empathetic show more altruism and students who are more honest have higher levels of pro-social behaviour (Allgaier et al 2015; Litvack-Miller et al. 1997).",
    "However, other studies have demonstrated that students are less likely to feel empathy if they believe another student has tried to gain an unfair advantage, (such as adjusting their grades on official documents) (Pupovac et al. 2019; Yachison et al. 2018), which some students in the present study felt GAI technologies facilitated.",
